34 SUMMARY
3355 This resolution proposes to amend the Constitution of Maine to provide that the right
3366 of the people to hunt, fish and harvest game and fish, including by the use of traditional
3377 methods, may not be infringed, subject to reasonable laws and rules to promote wildlife
3388 conservation and management and to preserve the future of hunting and fishing. It also
